        Defer
        ============
        Add a simple golang-esque deferral system for python.
        
        # Usage
        
        ```
        @defer.with_defer
        def example_function(defer):
            print("Hello")
            defer(print, "!")
            print("World")
            
        example_function()
        > Hello
        > World
        > !
        ```
